Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.83,0:01:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長大了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽比拿可說了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.58,0:01:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了人體鍊成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.94,0:01:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今你回來幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.38,0:01:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經沒有你的立身之處了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.95,0:01:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼燒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我決定了不再回頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了表示我們的覺悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.59,0:02:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不想再看到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.86,0:02:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想逃避不堪回首的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想掩蓋自己所犯下的過錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這和晚上尿床的小孩把床單藏起來是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃避了 愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.58,0:02:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我年輕的時候一模一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:43.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}墓前的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.91,0:03:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是老樣子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和以前完全一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.53,0:03:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不早點回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朵莉夏一直在等你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比拿可
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我兒子們鍊成的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是朵莉夏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有形成人形
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不能說是朵莉夏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是那個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 眼睛的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.49,0:04:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想說那不是朵莉夏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.38,0:04:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了製作完全無關的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個孩子失去了身體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.99,0:04:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用吃飯睡覺 一直能動？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.98,0:04:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 只要這個印記完好無損的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.70,0:04:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全就是不老不死嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:41.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.81,0:04:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是裝了個不定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:45.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.96,0:04:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴利說了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來不同人之間的靈魂和肉體是無法相容的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬是放到一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會產生拒絕反應
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那會是明天還是10年後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.41,0:05:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 不馬上恢復原來的身體就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 如果覺得身體不妙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.61,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能把靈魂轉移到別的東西上繼續生存嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.70,0:05:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使維持現狀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也感受不到疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:21.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不需要食物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.60,0:05:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個身體不是很方便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫莉 我進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 每次都是哥哥或者溫莉先生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:06:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都沒機會生氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.93,0:06:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個身體無法睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠恢復原來的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.04,0:06:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.44,0:06:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還回來 我弟弟的身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.30,0:06:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我唯一的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給你？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.86,0:06:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把弟弟變成那種身體的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:49.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華·愛力克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.15,0:06:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德華
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.78,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽不要這種身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德 還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.94,0:07:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父親要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能拿走這張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.87,0:07:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個人一起照的只有這張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為回禮 告訴妳一個好消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家馬上要發生很糟的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃去別的國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的事情又不少見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一些小傢伙把這裡當作歸宿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說我沒忠告過妳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.63,0:08:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也回來吃個飯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.52,0:08:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遺憾 比拿可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計再也吃不到妳做的飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要把那個挖出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要停手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手腳的銜接處在痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要下雨了 快點做完吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.49,0:09:31.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不確認的話就無法前進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.06,0:09:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.34,0:09:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.28,0:09:41.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼能逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆 媽媽的頭髮是棕色才對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.22,0:10:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿骨 太長了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.65,0:10:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是男人的骨盆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:10:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.16,0:11:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是你母親
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 死去的人無法復生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持清醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.37,0:11:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始 這就是絕望的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.24,0:11:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在卻和希望相連
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:11:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾能取回身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.52,0:12:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 這是卡迪斯家
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 是愛德嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.59,0:12:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有件事想問師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼 給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是師傅進行人體鍊成的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阿爾鍊成的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.29,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 你到底想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅鍊成的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是師傅的小孩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:27.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兒子們在戰場上好好幹了一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.73,0:13:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍恩海姆到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 他什麼也沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.08,0:13:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.46,0:13:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個重要的口信要給他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.61,0:13:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口信？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.26,0:13:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是朵莉夏的遺言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個人回來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.18,0:14:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我告訴他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法遵守約定
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.82,0:14:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先走一步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.56,0:14:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.47,0:14:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約定？是什麼約定？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.94,0:14:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.70,0:14:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 如果遇到那傢伙替我轉告他一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.71,0:14:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要我來？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別看他那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是很關心你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.03,0:14:29.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揍他一拳之後我再轉告他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.34,0:14:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回中央都市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.55,0:14:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 去被阿爾臭駡一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.76,0:14:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我一個人幹了不少事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.67,0:14:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.12,0:14:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.92,0:14:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然壞成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.59,0:14:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:14:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.36,0:14:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 出了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人 劊子手巴利？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有無法相容的身體和靈魂之間的拒絕反應嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剩下的鎧甲拉長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾能取回原來的身體吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.32,0:15:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了能恢復就能恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.54,0:15:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在利塞布爾 我把那時我們鍊成的東西挖出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼做這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.31,0:15:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從結果來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.89,0:16:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判明了那個不是媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.50,0:16:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們鍊成了完全不同的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.40,0:16:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.27,0:16:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 我獲得了能取回你身體的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.92,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在談這個話題之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.29,0:16:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫…溫莉 那個
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.77,0:16:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是否記得我們兄弟倆因為誰要娶妳而吵架
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前在屋頂上說過的話題？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說妳把阿爾甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.33,0:16:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 甩了 甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 有事要問你們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.48,0:16:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳甩了他的理由是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要比我身高還低的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用身高決定男人的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.13,0:17:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 這和阿爾的身體有什麼關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 阿爾知道我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同樣的事情溫莉也記得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.52,0:17:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說那是真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為記得真正存在的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.54,0:17:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以固定在鎧甲上的是真正的阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.75,0:17:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那扇門裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只有靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算是把你成功地拉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果靈魂能拉出來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也應該能把肉體從門裡拉回來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和靈魂分離 並且肉體還存在著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劊子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾 想想看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.06,0:17:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.05,0:17:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拉進真理之中的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.45,0:17:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.05,0:18:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以和靈魂一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.42,0:18:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把肉體也拉出來就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.91,0:18:10.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從被認為是媽媽的那個東西裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡面的 原來是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計是因為拒絕反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靈魂沒有固定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 我們沒有傷害任何人的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛力克先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊茲米·卡迪斯小姐打來的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調查了我的家譜和丈夫的家譜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.20,0:18:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鍊成出來的孩子的膚色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.94,0:18:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭髮的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我們夫婦之間無法產生的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你查到什麼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復阿爾身體的信心和…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓死去的人復生是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.41,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是缺少什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來就是做不到的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.23,0:19:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,師傅說了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.04,0:19:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說了「謝謝」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.90,0:19:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.20,0:19:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那天開始就一直在責備自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把媽媽變成那種樣子的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:19:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.19,0:20:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並沒有殺死媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.66,0:20:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊茲米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.92,0:20:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺被拯救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:18.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有第二次殺死那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我把你的身體變成了那樣是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什麼 我都要把你的身體恢復…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.35,0:20:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.47,0:20:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贊同了那種做法的我也是同罪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.52,0:20:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老是滿口自己一個人來背負的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼都自己一個人背
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.13,0:20:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不想再因為自己的事情而讓別人犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯先生也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當知道他死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.38,0:20:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就在想 如果要犧牲別人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:20:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不恢復身體也行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.33,0:21:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們看過許多 即使有著不是人的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.96,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也以自己的風格活著的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是這種身體 周圍的人也把我當人一樣對待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.23,0:21:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是定時炸彈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.31,0:21:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活生生的身體也一樣會有預料不到的生老病死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 想普通地生活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.16,0:21:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個身體也沒有任何不方便
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經能這樣想了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.77,0:21:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經 已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.82,0:21:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再度過獨自一人的夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.88,0:21:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.63,0:21:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想恢復身體的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 讓我們幹一場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢飛真理那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.62,0:22:05.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再把你的身體拉出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.47,0:22:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的背影有那麼高大嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷同伴的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使男人的步伐加速
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.24,0:24:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年為了走出死胡同
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.58,0:24:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加了乾坤一擲的勝敗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.30,0:24:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 鋼之鍊金術師
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.91,0:24:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.68,0:24:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第21話 愚者的前進
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.99,0:24:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥的帷幕由自己拉開
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
