Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:12.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即將起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.47,0:00:21.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:24.47,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:30.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不斷變化的地圖裡 攙雜著各種夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.55,0:00:32.94,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:37.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我這微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.04,0:00:43.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那雲的彼端嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.09,0:00:44.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}卻受了傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.29,0:00:49.34,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}彷彿看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}從天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.87,0:00:53.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}點點雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.05,0:00:56.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反復的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}筆直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.15,0:01:01.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.90,0:01:05.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}並不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.43,0:01:06.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.72,0:01:08.32,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:14.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的殘影烙印在兩眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:16.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在這片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:19.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}無論身在何處
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.32,0:01:22.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到達
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.18,0:01:27.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾見過的世界
